data.description: Say YES to this BELMONT ADDRESS! PRICE IMPROVEMENT, MOTIVATED SELLER! This home and community will WOW you from the time you pull in!! This open floorplan has everything you need to entertain in your home from the large island in the kitchen to extended lanai with no backyard neighbors and completely fenced. Here is a little peek into what you would be buying—A home with new luxury vinyl plank flooring, a new AC unit, split bedroom floorplan, open concept with lots of natural light and no carpet throughout the entire house! The Belmont Community has amazing amenities including pools, dog parks, playgrounds, and walk trails. Easy access to shopping, dining, YMCA, hospitals, Raymond James stadium, Tampa airport, with easy commutability to Tampa, Clearwater, St. Petersburg, and Sarasota. Make an appointment to see this home today!
